OL,3,CDrivers caught breaking law by police
OL,4,Cpatrolling in lorry cab
OL,6,FPolice officers have caught dozens of
OL,7,Fdrivers breaking the law while
OL,8,Fpatrolling around Bournemouth and
OL,9,FPoole in a lorry cab.
OL,11,FIn total, 120 offences were detected.
OL,12,FThe most common was not wearing a
OL,13,Fseatbelt, with 45 offences.
OL,15,F33 people were seen using a mobile
OL,16,Fphone whist driving and 10 motorists
OL,17,Fwere deemed not to be in proper
OL,18,Fcontrol of their vehicle.
