OL,3,CDrivers caught breaking law by police
OL,4,Cpatrolling in lorry cab
OL,6,FFive vehicles were seized and there
OL,7,Fwere three arrests for criminal
OL,8,Foffences.
OL,10,FUsing a mobile phone whilst driving,
OL,11,Fmeans six points and a #200 fine for
OL,12,Fguilty drivers.
OL,14,FDrivers caught not wearing a seatbelt
OL,15,Fcould be offered a driver's awareness
OL,16,Fcourse.
OL,18,FIt is the first time Dorset police has
OL,19,Fused the method of patrolling in a
OL,20,Florry cab.
