OL,3,CDrivers caught breaking law by police
OL,4,Cpatrolling in lorry cab
OL,6,FThe cab is seen as an ideal raised
OL,7,Fplatform to identify offences such as
OL,8,Fusing a mobile phones and not wearing
OL,9,Fa seatbelt.
OL,11,FThe week-long Operation Tramline used
OL,12,Fa lorry provided by National Highways,
OL,13,Fone of three being used by police
OL,14,Fforces around the country.
OL,16,FIf a driver is spotted breaking the
OL,17,Flaw, the officer in the lorry cab
OL,18,Falerts a following unmarked police
OL,19,Fcar, which then pulls over the
OL,20,Foffending motorist.
