OL,3,CDrivers caught breaking law by police
OL,4,Cpatrolling in lorry cab
OL,6,FInspector Joe Wheable from Dorset
OL,7,Fpolice said: "We often get reports
OL,8,Ffrom the public that we are not seeing
OL,9,Fthese offences.
OL,11,F"By being up higher and looking down
OL,12,Finto those vehicles and being able to
OL,13,Fuse the recording equipment, we can
OL,14,Fwitness those offences that we would
OL,15,Fnot otherwise normally see."
OL,17,FPart of the success of the operation
OL,18,Fis the publicity it generates, by
OL,19,Fmaking drivers more aware that there
OL,20,Fcould be someone watching them from
OL,21,Fany of the vehicles around them.
